{"tid":2185460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑又抽：林鄭應以國安法通緝捷克全體訪台議員","createTime":"2020-09-02T09:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T14:51:31.000Z","uid":9845,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7468afc443a0eabc474e924028aa70e24d7964cb","tid":2185460,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/4269014156504408/?extid=QeRDFMj0aEKmlExP&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F4269014156504408%2F%3Fextid%3DQeRDFMj0aEKmlExP%26d%3Dn&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXPTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=d2133b10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/4269014156504408/?extid=QeRDFMj0aEKmlExP&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"43316e0c8d5a9df1134278a3e0d52855a253e5e0","tid":2185460,"uid":9845,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"有一疑問：請問特首林鄭月娥是否應以香港國家安全委員會主席身份，向訪問台灣、並在台北立法院呼喊「我是台灣人」及「台灣是事實獨立的國家」、公然分裂中國領土的捷克參議院議長韋德齊及其訪台代表團全體議員，發出通緝令？<br />\n<br />\n韋德奇是否犯有港版國安法第二十條 ：任何人組織、策實施或者參與實施以下旨在分裂國家、破壞國家統一行為之一的，不論是否使用武力或者以武力相威脅，即屬犯罪？<br />\n<br />\n另根據第三十八條 ：不具有香港特別行政區永久性居民身份的人在香港特別行政區以外針對香港特別行政區實施本法規定的犯罪的，適用本法。<br />\n<br />\n不論三權分不分立，特區政府是否應依法宣示立場？"},{"pid":"2a4308210e6054737ba68f9e4c529b3180543599","tid":2185460,"uid":9845,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"我是台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9982d8a1501ed531eabece0ab17a2975bd41e91b","tid":2185460,"uid":9845,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">不論三權分不分立，特區政府是否應依法宣示立場？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921fd5280b1d4eb1a1e45df279589356ed6dbc08","tid":2185460,"uid